4590 if (status == TDEFL_STATUS_DONE)
4591 {
4592 result = MZ_TRUE(1);
4593 break;
4594 }
4595 else if (status != TDEFL_STATUS_OKAY)
4596 break;
4597 }
4598
4599 pZip->m_pFree(pZip->m_pAlloc_opaque, pComp);
4600
4601 if (!result)
4602 {
4603 pZip->m_pFree(pZip->m_pAlloc_opaque, pRead_buf);
4604 MZ_FCLOSEfclose(pSrc_file);
4605 return MZ_FALSE(0);
4606 }
4607
4608 comp_size = state.m_comp_size;
4609 cur_archive_file_ofs = state.m_cur_archive_file_ofs;
4610
4611 method = MZ_DEFLATED8;
4612 }
4613
4614 pZip->m_pFree(pZip->m_pAlloc_opaque, pRead_buf);
4615 }
4616
4617 MZ_FCLOSEfclose(pSrc_file); pSrc_file = NULL((void*)0);
4618
4619 // no zip64 support yet
4620 if ((comp_size > 0xFFFFFFFF) || (cur_archive_file_ofs > 0xFFFFFFFF))
4621 return MZ_FALSE(0);
4622
4623 if (!mz_zip_writer_create_local_dir_header(pZip, local_dir_header, (mz_uint16)archive_name_size, 0, uncomp_size, comp_size, uncomp_crc32, method, 0, dos_time, dos_date))
4624 return MZ_FALSE(0);
4625
4626 if (pZip->m_pWrite(pZip->m_pIO_opaque, local_dir_header_ofs, local_dir_header, sizeof(local_dir_header)) != sizeof(local_dir_header))
4627 return MZ_FALSE(0);
4628
4629 if (!mz_zip_writer_add_to_central_dir(pZip, pArchive_name, (mz_uint16)archive_name_size, NULL((void*)0), 0, pComment, comment_size, uncomp_size, comp_size, uncomp_crc32, method, 0, dos_time, dos_date, local_dir_header_ofs, ext_attributes))
4630 return MZ_FALSE(0);
4631
4632 pZip->m_total_files++;
4633 pZip->m_archive_size = cur_archive_file_ofs;
4634
4635 return MZ_TRUE(1);
4636}

4640{

4643 mz_uint64 cur_src_file_ofs, cur_dst_file_ofs;

& (pZip->m_file_offset_alignment - 1)) == 0) ; else __assert_fail
("(local_dir_header_ofs & (pZip->m_file_offset_alignment - 1)) == 0"
, "/work/repo/external/CppMicroServices/third_party/miniz.c",
4675, __extension__ __PRETTY_FUNCTION__); })); }
4676

4678 return MZ_FALSE(0);
4679 cur_dst_file_ofs += MZ_ZIP_LOCAL_DIR_HEADER_SIZE;

)) + MZ_READ_LE16(pLocal_header + MZ_ZIP_LDH_EXTRA_LEN_OFS)*((const mz_uint16 *)(pLocal_header + MZ_ZIP_LDH_EXTRA_LEN_OFS

):(comp_bytes_remaining));

4718 if (pZip->m_pWrite(pZip->m_pIO_opaque, cur_dst_file_ofs, pBuf, n) != n)

4721 return MZ_FALSE(0);

4725 cur_dst_file_ofs += n;
4726 }

), (mz_uint32)(local_dir_header_ofs));
4737 if (!mz_zip_array_push_back(pZip, &pState->m_central_dir, central_header, MZ_ZIP_CENTRAL_DIR_HEADER_SIZE))
4738 return MZ_FALSE(0);
4739
4740 n = MZ_READ_LE16(pSrc_central_header + MZ_ZIP_CDH_FILENAME_LEN_OFS)*((const mz_uint16 *)(pSrc_central_header + MZ_ZIP_CDH_FILENAME_LEN_OFS

));
4741 if (!mz_zip_array_push_back(pZip, &pState->m_central_dir, pSrc_central_header + MZ_ZIP_CENTRAL_DIR_HEADER_SIZE, n))
4742 {
4743 mz_zip_array_resize(pZip, &pState->m_central_dir, orig_central_dir_size, MZ_FALSE(0));
4744 return MZ_FALSE(0);
4745 }

4748 return MZ_FALSE(0);
4749 n = (mz_uint32)orig_central_dir_size;
4750 if (!mz_zip_array_push_back(pZip, &pState->m_central_dir_offsets, &n, 1))
4751 {
4752 mz_zip_array_resize(pZip, &pState->m_central_dir, orig_central_dir_size, MZ_FALSE(0));
4753 return MZ_FALSE(0);
4754 }

4762mz_bool mz_zip_writer_finalize_archive(mz_zip_archive *pZip)
4763{
4764 mz_zip_internal_state *pState;
4765 mz_uint64 central_dir_ofs, central_dir_size;
4766 mz_uint8 hdr[MZ_ZIP_END_OF_CENTRAL_DIR_HEADER_SIZE];
4767
4768 if ((!pZip) || (!pZip->m_pState) || (pZip->m_zip_mode != MZ_ZIP_MODE_WRITING))
4769 return MZ_FALSE(0);
4770
4771 pState = pZip->m_pState;
4772
4773 // no zip64 support yet
4774 if ((pZip->m_total_files > 0xFFFF) || ((pZip->m_archive_size + pState->m_central_dir.m_size + MZ_ZIP_END_OF_CENTRAL_DIR_HEADER_SIZE) > 0xFFFFFFFF))
4775 return MZ_FALSE(0);
4776
4777 central_dir_ofs = 0;
4778 central_dir_size = 0;
4779 if (pZip->m_total_files)
4780 {
4781 // Write central directory
4782 central_dir_ofs = pZip->m_archive_size;
4783 central_dir_size = pState->m_central_dir.m_size;
4784 pZip->m_central_directory_file_ofs = central_dir_ofs;
4785 if (pZip->m_pWrite(pZip->m_pIO_opaque, central_dir_ofs, pState->m_central_dir.m_p, (size_t)central_dir_size) != central_dir_size)
4786 return MZ_FALSE(0);
4787 pZip->m_archive_size += central_dir_size;
4788 }
4789
4790 // Write end of central directory record
4791 MZ_CLEAR_OBJ(hdr)memset(&(hdr), 0, sizeof(hdr));
4792 MZ_WRITE_LE32(hdr + MZ_ZIP_ECDH_SIG_OFS, MZ_ZIP_END_OF_CENTRAL_DIR_HEADER_SIG)mz_write_le32((mz_uint8 *)(hdr + MZ_ZIP_ECDH_SIG_OFS), (mz_uint32
)(MZ_ZIP_END_OF_CENTRAL_DIR_HEADER_SIG));
4793 MZ_WRITE_LE16(hdr + MZ_ZIP_ECDH_CDIR_NUM_ENTRIES_ON_DISK_OFS, pZip->m_total_files)mz_write_le16((mz_uint8 *)(hdr + MZ_ZIP_ECDH_CDIR_NUM_ENTRIES_ON_DISK_OFS
), (mz_uint16)(pZip->m_total_files));
4794 MZ_WRITE_LE16(hdr + MZ_ZIP_ECDH_CDIR_TOTAL_ENTRIES_OFS, pZip->m_total_files)mz_write_le16((mz_uint8 *)(hdr + MZ_ZIP_ECDH_CDIR_TOTAL_ENTRIES_OFS
), (mz_uint16)(pZip->m_total_files));
4795 MZ_WRITE_LE32(hdr + MZ_ZIP_ECDH_CDIR_SIZE_OFS, central_dir_size)mz_write_le32((mz_uint8 *)(hdr + MZ_ZIP_ECDH_CDIR_SIZE_OFS), (
mz_uint32)(central_dir_size));
4796 MZ_WRITE_LE32(hdr + MZ_ZIP_ECDH_CDIR_OFS_OFS, central_dir_ofs)mz_write_le32((mz_uint8 *)(hdr + MZ_ZIP_ECDH_CDIR_OFS_OFS), (
mz_uint32)(central_dir_ofs));
4797
4798 if (pZip->m_pWrite(pZip->m_pIO_opaque, pZip->m_archive_size, hdr, sizeof(hdr)) != sizeof(hdr))
4799 return MZ_FALSE(0);
4800#ifndef MINIZ_NO_STDIO
4801 if ((pState->m_pFile) && (MZ_FFLUSHfflush(pState->m_pFile) == EOF(-1)))
4802 return MZ_FALSE(0);
4803#endif // #ifndef MINIZ_NO_STDIO
4804
4805 pZip->m_archive_size += sizeof(hdr);
4806
4807 pZip->m_zip_mode = MZ_ZIP_MODE_WRITING_HAS_BEEN_FINALIZED;
4808 return MZ_TRUE(1);
4809}
4810
4811mz_bool mz_zip_writer_finalize_heap_archive(mz_zip_archive *pZip, void **pBuf, size_t *pSize)
4812{
4813 if ((!pZip) || (!pZip->m_pState) || (!pBuf) || (!pSize))
4814 return MZ_FALSE(0);
4815 if (pZip->m_pWrite != mz_zip_heap_write_func)
4816 return MZ_FALSE(0);
4817 if (!mz_zip_writer_finalize_archive(pZip))
4818 return MZ_FALSE(0);
4819
4820 *pBuf = pZip->m_pState->m_pMem;
4821 *pSize = pZip->m_pState->m_mem_size;
4822 pZip->m_pState->m_pMem = NULL((void*)0);
4823 pZip->m_pState->m_mem_size = pZip->m_pState->m_mem_capacity = 0;
4824 return MZ_TRUE(1);
4825}
4826
4827mz_bool mz_zip_writer_end(mz_zip_archive *pZip)
4828{
4829 mz_zip_internal_state *pState;
4830 mz_bool status = MZ_TRUE(1);
4831 if ((!pZip) || (!pZip->m_pState) || (!pZip->m_pAlloc) || (!pZip->m_pFree) || ((pZip->m_zip_mode != MZ_ZIP_MODE_WRITING) && (pZip->m_zip_mode != MZ_ZIP_MODE_WRITING_HAS_BEEN_FINALIZED)))
4832 return MZ_FALSE(0);
4833
4834 pState = pZip->m_pState;
4835 pZip->m_pState = NULL((void*)0);

4855 pZip->m_zip_mode = MZ_ZIP_MODE_INVALID;
4856 return status;
